      <p>I love to build products that help people. I've co-founded <a href="work/flitsmeister">Flitsmeister</a> with Sjoerd Perfors and started <a href="http://govisual.nl">GoVisual</a> with him and Jaco de Vries while working at <a href="http://www.omnext.net">Omnext</a>. I recently built <a href="/work/dragshare">Dragshare for Dropbox</a>. You can find more of my personal projects in the <a href="/">work</a> section of this site.</p>




