      <h2>Some history</h2>

      <p>I started developing and designing websites in 1998. In 2000, I co-founded and built one of the biggest dutch music websites called 'Clubcharts'. When I finished school in 2007, I started working at <a href="http://www.omnext.net">Omnext</a>, where I've worked with bigger companies like IBM.</p>
      <p>Omnext is also the company where I met Sjoerd Perfors, with whom I started <a href="work/flitsmeister">Flitsmeister</a>, and Jaco de Vries who joined us together with Jorn de Vries to help us shape Flitsmeister into a profitable business.</p>
      <p>The last couple of years I have been focusing on designing for mobile and I've worked closely with several small startups, big companies but also individuals from all over the globe.</p>

